me.choco.locksecurity.utils

Class LSPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.choco.locksecurity.utils.LSPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONSerializable

    public class LSPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONSerializable
    A wrapper class for the OfflinePlayer interface containing information about a player's LockSecurity details such as (but not limited to); their data file, their owned blocks, their active modes (LSMode), etc.

    NOTE: Information regarding owned locked blocks is a record of what locked blocks currently exist. Not all owned blocks are registered in the LockedBlockManager, meaning unregistered blocks will be ignored in a locked block lookup / protection listener

    Author:
    Parker Hawke - 2008Choco
